title: Brexit, Trade & Impeachment

description:
Guest host June Grasso spoke with Marc Ross, CEO of Caracal Global, Emily Wilkins, Bloomberg Government Congress reporter and Eli Yokley, Political reporter for Morning Consult.

They discussed impeachment, Brexit, trade and congressional elections.
